messages.message: Is there some way to see the current AI Hub version number in the platform? If not, maybe we could include it under the *?* icon in the top nav bar. I think it would help users when reviewing our release notes to be able to easily identify the current version, particularly if/when we start marking any known issues as present or resolved in release _xx.xx_.

I asked for this here too:
https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C0516UPPMT3/p1694087236236909
